00:04:05,902 --> 00:04:07,821
Masako...! Long
time no see!

52
00:04:07,904 --> 00:04:09,447
How are you?

53
00:04:09,531 --> 00:04:11,574
Is Naru here?

54
00:04:11,658 --> 00:04:13,827
Well, Good to
see you too!

55
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:15,328
Sorry...

56
00:04:15,412 --> 00:04:16,913
I just decided to drop in
because there's a case

57
00:04:16,996 --> 00:04:19,290
I came across that
Naru may like.

58
00:04:20,625 --> 00:04:23,086
So, what is it you
wanted to talk about?

59
