A friend from
the TV station

60
00:04:24,546 --> 00:04:26,673
has specifically
requested your help.

61
00:04:26,756 --> 00:04:28,383
Apparently, there's been
a strange phenomenon

62
00:04:28,466 --> 00:04:31,052
