00:06:28,545 --> 00:06:31,673
We have yet to determine
if it's a spirit or not.

116
00:06:31,756 --> 00:06:34,426
I assume that's what we're
about to investigate right?

117
00:06:34,509 --> 00:06:35,927
Where's Matsuzaki?

118
00:06:36,011 --> 00:06:39,556
Uhh, I called her but I guess
she must be running late.

119
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:41,516
You know how she is.

120
00:06:41,599 --> 00:06:43,977
She'll waltz in here and
say something like...

121
00:06:44,060 --> 00:06:46,354
This is clearly the work
of an earth spirit

122
00:06:46,438 --> 00:06:49,107
Wow Monk! That
was perfect!

123
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:51,609
This is clearly the work
of an earth spirit

124
00:06:57,073 --> 00:06:58,616
Care to fill me in on
what's so funny?

125
00:07:00,452 --> 00:07:03,079
Now that we're all here let's
begin the investigation

126
00:07:03,163 --> 00:07:05,331
This is a case
about a phenomenon

127
00:07:05,415 --> 00:07:08,293
that only happens under
specific circumstances,

128
00:07:08,376 --> 00:07:10,003
which means that you
will all have to...

129
00:07:10,086 --> 00:07:12,505
Yeah we know. Get to
the point already...

130
00:07:12,589 --> 00:07:14,591
We'll exorcise
the spirit, right?

131
00:07:14,674 --> 00:07:17,218
Huh...? I'm not about to
do my ritual out here

132
00:07:17,302 --> 00:07:19,179
in front of all
these families.

133
00:07:19,262 --> 00:07:22,640
For this case exorcisms
will not be necessary.

134
00:07:22,724 --> 00:07:25,352
Then what exactly do
you plan for us to do?

135
00:07:25,435 --> 00:07:27,771
The plan is to have you
all act as live bait.

136
00:07:27,854 --> 00:07:29,064
Bait?

137
00:07:29,147 --> 00:07:30,857
The term sounds worse
than it really is,

138
00:07:30,940 --> 00:07:33,860
however it's the quickest way
to draw out the spirit.

139
00:07:33,943 --> 00:07:35,445
I have a feeling this was
your goal from the start,

140
00:07:35,528 --> 00:07:37,238
wasn't it Masako?

141
00:07:37,322 --> 00:07:38,656
Now we just have to
divide ourselves

142
00:07:38,740 --> 00:07:40,367
into three bait couples.

143
00:07:40,450 --> 00:07:41,701
Hey Mai...

144
00:07:41,785 --> 00:07:45,080
