score a date with Naru.

145
00:07:45,163 --> 00:07:46,539
He's right.

146
00:07:46,623 --> 00:07:47,874
I better...

147
00:07:47,957 --> 00:07:50,251
Okay! I'm in!

148
00:07:50,335 --> 00:07:54,381
Alright. I think Naru and I
should be the first team.

149
00:07:54,464 --> 00:07:56,800
Ayako , You suck,!!

150
00:07:56,883 --> 00:07:59,010
I'm the only girl here who
doesn't look out of place

151
00:07:59,094 --> 00:08:00,428
on Naru's arm...

152
